                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Peirce</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-08-25"><hi rend="italic">August 25,
                                1900</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>[Mr. Adee authorizes Mr. Peirce to sign the protocol with the addition
                            indicated in his cablegram of the 24th instant.]</p>
